OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FDespite airspaces only being partially
OL,7,Fclosed in Saudi Arabia and the United
OL,8,FArab Emirates, very few flights are
OL,9,Fleaving the countries' airports for
OL,10,Fthe UK, ITV News Consumer Editor Chris
OL,11,FChoi reports
OL,13,FThe war in Iran has left hundreds of
OL,14,Fthousands of British citizens stranded
OL,15,Fin the Middle East, as airspaces are
OL,16,Fclosed across the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
