OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FThe renewed fighting hasn't just
OL,7,Faffected those trying to leave the
OL,8,Farea, but the millions of passengers
OL,9,Fthat travel through major transport
OL,10,Fhubs like Dubai Airport each year, as
OL,11,Fthey connect flights from Europe,
OL,12,FAsia, Australasia and Africa.
OL,14,FAs the conflict widens to countries
OL,15,Fincluding Cyprus, where an RAF site
OL,16,Fwas the target of a drone attack, many
OL,17,Fare questioning whether it is safe to
OL,18,Ftravel to areas that could be
OL,19,Fpotential targets of strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
