OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FSo what restrictions are in place, and
OL,7,Fwhat is the advice for those hoping to
OL,8,Ftravel?
OL,10,FThe Middle East
OL,12,FThere are multiple countries that have
OL,13,Frestrictions in place. Of these, the
OL,14,Fmajority have a total closure of
OL,15,Fairspace, meaning it is incredibly
OL,16,Fdifficult to travel in or out of the
OL,17,Fcountries:
OL,19,FOthers have a partial closure, meaning
OL,20,Ftravel is still heavily restricted:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
