CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FWhile Lebanese airspace remains
OL,7,Fpartially open, the Foreign,
OL,8,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,9,F(FCDO) has advised against all travel
OL,10,Fin some areas of Beirut and its
OL,11,Fsouthern suburbs, and it has urged
OL,12,FBritish nationals currently in Lebanon
OL,13,Fto sign up for travel alerts and
OL,14,Ffollow instructions from local
OL,15,Fauthorities.
OL,17,FQatar Airways has suspended flights
OL,18,Funtil Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
