PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FA limited number of repatriation
OL,7,Fflights for British nationals and
OL,8,Fcitizens from EU countries will
OL,9,Foperate on Thursday.
OL,11,FBritish Airways flights from Muscat
OL,12,Fare fully booked until Saturday.
OL,14,FDespite airspaces only being partially
OL,15,Fclosed in Saudi Arabia and the United
OL,16,FArab Emirates, very few flights are
OL,17,Fleaving the countries' airports for
OL,18,Fthe UK. Airlines have said the
OL,19,Fsituation is being closely monitored
OL,20,Fand could be subject to change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
