OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FSome airlines have advised passengers
OL,7,Fnot to attend the airport unless they
OL,8,Fhave been contacted directly, and to
OL,9,Fkeep up to date with the latest travel
OL,10,Fupdates on the airlines' websites.
OL,12,FBritish nationals in Bahrain, Israel,
OL,13,FKuwait, Palestine, Qatar and the
OL,14,FUnited Arab Emirates are advised by
OL,15,Fthe Government to register their
OL,16,Fpresence in the region, in order to
OL,17,Freceive direct updates from the
OL,18,FForeign, Commonwealth and Development
OL,19,FOffice (FCDO).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
