OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FYou should also continue to follow the
OL,7,Ftravel advice for the country you are
OL,8,Fin, and keep up to date with advice
OL,9,Ffrom the local authorities.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHoliday destinations like Turkey,
OL,17,FEgypt and Cyprus are largely
OL,18,Funaffected and remain open, as the
OL,19,Fmajority of airstrikes remain centred
OL,20,Faround the Gulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
