CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FHowever, travellers are advised to
OL,7,Fstay vigilant to any changing travel
OL,8,Fcircumstances and keep up to date with
OL,9,Fadvice from the Foreign Office.
OL,11,FAs of Thursday, foreign office advice
OL,12,Ffor Turkey remains unchanged for
OL,13,Ftravellers arriving from the UK, and
OL,14,Fareas with popular holiday resorts are
OL,15,Fnot affected by the conflict in the
OL,16,FGulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
