OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FFlights are still operating between
OL,7,FTurkey and the UK, but passengers
OL,8,Fshould check the airline's latest
OL,9,Fadvice before leaving for the airport,
OL,10,Fas the situation could change rapidly.
OL,12,FThe government does warn that regional
OL,13,Fescalation poses significant security
OL,14,Frisks and has led to travel
OL,15,Fdisruption. Travellers are advised to
OL,16,Ffamiliarise themselves with the
OL,17,FGovernment's guidance on "how to
OL,18,Fprepare for a crisis", follow advice
OL,19,Ffrom authorities, and ensure their
OL,20,Ftravel documents are up to date.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
