OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office advice for travel
OL,7,Fto Egypt has not changed since the
OL,8,Fconflict erupted, but visitors should
OL,9,Fstay informed before travelling. The
OL,10,Fsituation is also subject to rapid
OL,11,Fchanges if the war escalates further
OL,12,Finto the region.
OL,14,FFlights are still operating between
OL,15,FEgypt and the UK, but passengers
OL,16,Fshould check the airline's latest
OL,17,Fadvice before leaving for the airport,
OL,18,Fas the situation could change rapidly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
