PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FThere have been a number of flight
OL,7,Fcancellations to and from Cyprus,
OL,8,Fparticularly since the drone attack on
OL,9,Fthe RAF base, so passengers should
OL,10,Fstay notified of any updates from
OL,11,Ftheir airline.
OL,13,FCypriot officials previously
OL,14,Fcriticised the UK Government for not
OL,15,Fdoing enough to defend the island amid
OL,16,Fthe attack.
OL,18,FBritain's lack of military assets in
OL,19,Fthe Middle East have also been
OL,20,Fscrutinised and are accusations which
OL,21,FDowning Street has rejected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
