PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FIt was put to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer's spokesperson that the UK was
OL,8,Fnot fully prepared, which the
OL,9,Fspokesperson refuted.
OL,11,FThe official responded: "I don't
OL,12,Faccept that. I think the fact is,
OL,13,Foperational questions, operational
OL,14,Fdecision-making is always kept under
OL,15,Freview."
OL,17,FWhat travel protections are you
OL,18,Fentitled to?
OL,26,@sD@YOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FWhile the foreign office still deems
OL,7,Fareas in Turkey, Egypt and Cyprus safe
OL,8,Fto travel and tourism continues,
OL,9,Fdisruption is still very possible.
OL,11,FUnder UK law, if you are departing
OL,12,Ffrom an airport in the UK on any
OL,13,Fairline, or arriving at an EU or UK
OL,14,Fairport on an EU or UK airline, you
OL,15,Fhave legal rights if your flight is
OL,16,Fcancelled.
OL,18,FYour airline is legally required to
OL,19,Foffer you an alternative flight at the
OL,20,Fearliest opportunity or a full refund
OL,21,Fif your flight is cancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FHowever, you may not be entitled to
OL,7,Fadditional compensation, as
OL,8,Fcancellations relating to war will
OL,9,Ffall under "extraordinary
OL,10,Fcircumstances."
OL,12,FIf the delay for a new flight is over
OL,13,Ftwo hours, the airline must provide
OL,14,Fyou with care and support, such as
OL,15,Fmeals and refreshments, or hotel
OL,16,Faccommodation and transport to the
OL,17,Faccommodation if an overnight stay is
OL,18,Fwarranted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772716281
OL,3,CIran war: Where is safe to travel, and
OL,4,Cwhat are your rights?
OL,6,FIf your flight to the UK is cancelled
OL,7,Fand you are travelling with a non-UK
OL,8,For non-EU airline, you are not covered
OL,9,Funder this legislation and will have
OL,10,Fto check the local airline laws and
OL,11,Fpolicies.
OL,13,FIf you booked a package holiday
OL,14,Fthrough a UK tour operator and the
OL,15,FFCDO deems your location unsafe, or
OL,16,Fflight delays and cancellations mean
OL,17,Fyou can't attend, then your operator
OL,18,Fmust offer an alternative holiday if
OL,19,Fpossible or refund you the full price.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
